# Table of Contents

# 1. Purpose of This Document

This document records every major technical and architectural decision made for B-Edge before writing a single line of production code. Each decision includes what was decided, why it was decided, which external source or competitor validated it, and exactly how B-Edge implements it.

This is a living reference. Every engineer (human or AI) working on B-Edge reads this document first. No decision documented here is revisited without a validated reason. No new architectural decision is made without being added here.

*⚡ A bug found during design costs $100 to fix. The same bug in production costs $10,000. Every decision here was made to avoid the $10,000 version.*

| **Category** | **Decisions made** | **Bugs pre-solved** | **Migration rules** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Technology stack | 6 | 0 | 0 |
| Database design | 8 | 11 | 7 |
